data.title: Flickr: Discussing Online Exhibit of Apostle Images in Apostles
data.meta_description: The safest and most inclusive global community of photography enthusiasts. The best place for inspiration, connection, and sharing!
data.text:
Reina y Madre del Ciudad de Parañaque says:

To all membersof Apostles: Though there are not much new posts in the group, I want to organize an exhibit related to the apostles.

Here are some rules:

1. Duplications are permitted

2. The picture you can post may be a statue, painting, relief etc.

3. The picture that you shall post may other people's santo, but when posting, please put their name below the photo.

To start, I have my Santiago Mayor Apostol
